%section#service.section-padding
  .container
    .row
      .col-md-4.col-sm-4
        %h2.ser-title Choose your loan
        %hr.botm-line/
        %p Many businesses need cash fast for POs, to expand, emergencies, or general opperations. Banks take time to process your application, fund you the loan, and have high intrest rates. Many go to alternative lenders but they get overcharged. We believe you should be able to see all your loan options before deciding on one.

      .col-md-4.col-sm-4
        .service-info
          .icon
            %i.fa.fa-clock-o
          .icon-info
            %h4 24 Hour Response
            %p We pride ourselves on how quickly we can have your loan approved with low rates. Our goal is to send you up to five loan quotes within 24 hours.
        .service-info
          .icon
            %i.fa.fa-money
          .icon-info
            %h4 Save Money
            %p Save up to 30% by compairing your options instead of going with traditional lenders.

      .col-md-4.col-sm-4
        .service-info
          .icon
            %i.fa.fa-check-square-o
          .icon-info
            %h4 Qualify in Minutes
            %p You can qualify in minutes without searching for the right lender or filling out paperwork. Leave the legwork to us!
        .service-info
          .icon
            %i.fa.fa-thumbs-up
          .icon-info
            %h4 Build Credit
            %p You can build your credit by getting a loan that won't drown you in interest. Get a loan you can afford!

